{
  "stem": "2316.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "That night-- that night it was already late in the evening by then.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We were 17 people in that wall, but three small children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And my cousin's youngest baby was crying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And the mother choked her because she wanted to save the other two little boys.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They were older.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "They understood better.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And I peeked out through the cracks of the wood.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "There was like pine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And nobody was allowed to cough, or cry, or breathe, actually, because Nazis were all over the place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And they were holding our mouths.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And if you wanted to sneeze, or something, they were choking us and putting, you know, stuff in our mouths not to sneeze, not to cough, not to talk.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I looked out at one point in the cracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "It was still daylight and they had a truck full of babies-- an open truck, not closed, just two sides and the back.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And there was two soldiers, or three-- two that I saw through the crack.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And they just kept-- what they did is they pick those babies by their arms, by their legs, as they were walking.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "They were still leading them to the ghetto and throwing them on the truck.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And the mothers were reaching and screaming and crying.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And I saw that and I just, I couldn't understand it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "What it was all about.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "I thought it wasn't for real.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Like I saw my little cousins baby, or my little cousin thrown on the truck.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, it's-- I don't know what we could have done.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Except that if I would run out they'd put me in the truck, too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, the feeling that I had, I can't explain to this day.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
